narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is a difficult class in that a lot of gramatical concepts are covered pretty quickly but if you have had some experience in high school with Spanish (2-3 years depending on your retention) then this class is manageable.
Yes, I would recommend this class&the professor to another student. It taught me more Spanish and Prof. Leon was helpful.
Take the class, its worth it.
I would highly recommend taking Spanish and taking it with Senora Leon.
I would summarize it as "intro college Spanish". I would recommend it to any student who wants a good foundation in the language.
